Complete and Publish Workspace

Add your app to the workspace

  1. Add another section.

  2. Click Add Widget.

  3. Click Tiles in the widget gallery.

  4. In the search box, start typing your AC username AC096819U21, select the Create Sales Order AC096819U21 app, and then click Add.

If you do not see your App appear when searching, please refresh the page and try again.

NOTE: If you have not created the build app as part of Build Apps TA, you can add the Generic Build App “TA - Sales Order Build App” as shown below.

 

  1. After saving the App the view looks like the image shown below.

    Your Build App Tile:

    Generic App Tile:

  2. Scroll to the top of your page and click Publish.

This is how your workspace looks - note that the AC096819U21 Create Sales Order app is under the header that you created:
